  "texts": [
    "In order to enhance the network's interpretability and visual comprehension, a Class activation mapping (CAM) module is incorporated into the ResNet architecture (as depicted in Fig. 2).",
    "The CAM module plays a crucial role in comprehending how the network allocates attention to different categories and identifies significant image regions.",
    "This network architecture facilitates both image classification and the generation of category activation maps simultaneously.",
    "This capability allows the network not only to predict the input image's category but also to provide visual interpretations of the classification outcomes.",
    "To enhance the analysis and comprehension of the feature extraction process within the network, as well as to support research and applications in feature visualization and analysis, the hook technique is utilized in conjunction with ResNet."
  ],
